text: Ivan Fesenko (born 22 August 1981) is a Russian skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 2006 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Russia Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 2006 Winter Olympics Category:People from Berezniki
